{
  "style": "",
  "texts": [
    "First, to ensure compatibility, the dimensions of the feature maps from the efficientNetV2 encoder are adjusted using a 1 × 1 convolutional layer to match the shapes of the feature maps from the ViTs encoder.",
    "Next, channel attention is applied to both sets of feature maps.",
    "This is achieved by passing the adjusted feature maps from the efficientNetV2 encoder and the feature maps from the ViTs encoder through the SE block.",
    "The SE block performs global average pooling on the input feature maps to obtain the global channel descriptors.",
    "These descriptors are then passed through two dense layers."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}